abstract: Academy of Nutrition and Dietetics says it is working with Kraft Foods Group to end part of deal that allowed Kraft to use one of academy's logos on packages of Kraft Singles cheese slices.
lead_paragraph: The Academy of Nutrition and Dietetics is working to terminate a deal that had allowed Kraft to affix the group’s Kids Eat Right label to its cheese slices.

headline.main: Dietitians Group Negotiating to End Labeling Deal With Kraft Singles
headline.print_headline: Dietitians Group Negotiating to End Labeling Deal With Kraft Singles
